Hook::Filter
============

Hook::Filter is a runtime firewall for subroutine calls.

See perldoc Hook::Filter for more information.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Module::Pluggable
  File::Spec

